Package neqsim.pvtsimulation.regression

Enum Class RegressionParameter

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<RegressionParameter>
neqsim.pvtsimulation.regression.RegressionParameter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<RegressionParameter>, Constable
public enum RegressionParameter extends Enum<RegressionParameter>
Enumeration of regression parameters for PVT model tuning.

Each parameter type includes default bounds and methods to apply the parameter to a fluid system.

Version:
1.0
Author:
ESOL
